{'id_' : 'le|go|me|m06|d19_swh_KE_oak|lemeLI|Gospel|text', 'text' : 'Bwana aliwaambia wanafunzi wake, "Azipokeaye amri zangu na kuzishika, yeye ndiye anipendaye. Naye anipendaye mimi atapendwa na Baba yangu, nami nitampenda na kujidhihirisha kwake." Yuda (si yule Iskarioti) akamwambia, "Bwana, itawezekanaje wewe kujidhihirisha kwetu na si kwa ulimwengu?" Yesu akamjibu, "Mtu akinipenda atashika neno langu, na Baba yangu atampenda, nasi tutakuja kwake na kukaa naye. Asiyenipenda hashiki maneno yangu. Na neno mlilosikia si langu, bali ni lake Baba aliyenituma."'}
